## Abas (Tab Panels) — ARIA Obrigatório

**PlaybookInfluencers** e páginas futuras com abas: semântica ARIA completa.

```tsx
<div
  role="tablist"
  aria-label="Descrição do grupo de abas"
  style={{ display: "flex", gap: 4, overflowX: "auto", scrollbarWidth: "none" }}
>
  {ABAS.map((aba) => (
    <button
      key={aba.key}
      type="button"
      role="tab"
      id={`tab-${aba.key}`}
      aria-selected={abaAtiva === aba.key}
      aria-controls={`panel-${aba.key}`}
      onClick={() => setAbaAtiva(aba.key)}
      style={{ ... }}
    >
      {aba.label}
    </button>
  ))}
</div>

<div
  role="tabpanel"
  id={`panel-${abaConfig.key}`}
  aria-labelledby={`tab-${abaConfig.key}`}
>
  {/* conteúdo */}
</div>
```

### Indicador de overflow em abas com scroll horizontal

```tsx
<div style={{ position: "relative" }}>
  <div style={{ display: "flex", gap: 4, overflowX: "auto", scrollbarWidth: "none" }}>
    {/* botões de aba */}
  </div>
  <div
    aria-hidden="true"
    style={{
      position: "absolute", right: 0, top: 0, bottom: 0,
      width: 60,
      background: `linear-gradient(to left, ${brand.blockBg ?? t.cardBg} 0%, transparent 100%)`,
      pointerEvents: "none",
    }}
  />
</div>
```

